text:
Mei Ching Chen (born 19 May 1985) is a Taiwanese volleyball player. She played for the Chinese Taipei women's national volleyball team. She played at the 2006 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship and 2006 Asian Games.
She played for National Kaohsiung Normal University's women's volleyball team.
